Merge pull request #2 from sjohannes/fix-crash-on-setprop-error

Fix segfault when property Set() call fails.
Fix segfault when property Set() call fails.
Port to Gtk3 >=3.2. Even debian wheezy has 3.4.

Rename mpris2_client_auto_set_player to mpris2_client_auto_connect.

Return a boolean to avoid possible memory leaks.

Fix a waring when init mpris2-status-icon.

Call g_type_init() when using so older versions as Debian Wheezy!.

In short, fix several seg faults!!!. :S
Add mpris2_client_get_available_players() public function.
Set metdata before send playback status.
Libmpris2client V0.1.0
Example: D'Oh!. Fix typos..
Example: Add loop_status and shuffle options.

Example: Always check connection before send action.
Alway remove old albumart when stop playback or close player.

Extract status-icon example from xfce4-soundmenu-plugin and put it here,
Update gitignore.

Init player as NULL, and when set NULL it disconnect client.
Also others changes that not remember where they came.

Add strict_mode setting disable by default.
Allows ignore CanGoNext, CanGoPrevious, etc, due they are not properly implemented in any player!.
Implement can_go_next, can_go_prev, can_play, can_pause, can_seek.
Implement can_control
